  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">Wizards looking for the segment of the Staff of the Wheel near the island: Go to the shipwreck, aligning yourself with the mast protruding from the water. Swim straight down and the rod is nearby (but not exactly where you'll end up).<br>
<br>
A high swimming skill is key: The rod is very deep and even with 125 Swimming I was about to start drowning when I surfaced after finding it. Bringing along a druid friend with Enduring Breath would be a wise idea.<br>
<br>
There are some sharks in the vicinity, although they aren't stationed near the rod. More of a pain is the fact that you'll have to go past the undead sailors. Kill them immediately before diving to make the trip go as smoothly as possible.<br><br></td></tr>
