  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">If you want to do this portion of the Shaman Epic quest... there is a very easy way to do it.  Levitate and run to the spawn point of the spirit (-1600, 4200).  At 30 minutes after talking to the ogre shaman on the island, the spirit will spawn and start casting.  You will see the casting message.  Swim down and go through the quest details - then leave.  I did not see any shark's at the quest location.<br>
<br>
Note: While lev'ed on the surface for 30 minutes I cast 'sense animals' several times and only found 'a shark', never plagues or killers.  They may have been removed - but be careful non-the-less.<br><br></td></tr>
